Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.46,0:01:42.31,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}どうしたら あなたに愛を刻めるんだろう？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.86,0:01:55.49,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}知らない気持ちばかり 覚えたよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.49,0:01:58.70,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}忘れかたも教えて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.74,0:02:04.91,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}言葉だけじゃなくてさ 震える指の温度から
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.04,0:02:11.50,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}それは誰の希望? 私から溢れ出した願いの雫（DROP）
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.50,0:02:15.05,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}消えても 消えても 生まれてくるけど
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.17,0:02:18.05,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}答えなき酷い未来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.47,0:02:24.18,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}何回目の明日が来るのか わからない夜なら
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.18,0:02:28.81,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}名前を呼ばれたい だって胸が痛い
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.81,0:02:32.77,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}痛くて張り裂けそうだ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.23,0:02:40.45,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}どうしたら あなたに愛を刻めるんだろう？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.61,0:02:46.33,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}私がいつか 空に溶け去る前に
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.33,0:02:53.88,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}強い想いで いまを守りたくなった
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.88,0:03:00.76,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}理由は あなたをもっと見ていたいから…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.46,0:01:42.31,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}如何才能在你心中  铭刻下我的爱意
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.86,0:01:55.49,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}是你  让我体会到无数不曾知晓的情感
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.49,0:01:58.70,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}告诉我该如何忘记吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.74,0:02:04.91,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}不要只是开口  用你颤抖的手指的温度告诉我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.04,0:02:11.50,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}又是谁的希望  让我眼眶中的泪水决堤
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.50,0:02:15.05,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}即便滑落脸庞  消失无踪  又会聚满眼眶
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.17,0:02:18.05,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}悲惨的未来里  我寻觅不到答案
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.47,0:02:24.18,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}长夜漫漫  不知道要第几次迎来明天时
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.18,0:02:28.81,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}总想听到你呼唤我的名字  只因揪紧的心口
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.81,0:02:32.77,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}撕心裂肺的痛苦  叫我不堪忍受
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.23,0:02:40.45,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}如何才能在你心中  铭刻下我的爱意
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.61,0:02:46.33,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}不要等到我  化作天边星辰的那一天
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.33,0:02:53.88,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}强烈的思念  催促我守护眼前的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.88,0:03:00.76,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}只因为还想多见到你  哪怕一分一秒
Comment: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,Comment,,0,0,0,,——IN1——
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.61,0:15:07.37,CQEG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3\an9\fs34}The life is not for comparing things
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.42,0:15:14.33,CQEG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3\an9\fs34}So I hold both the light and shadows
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.56,0:15:22.79,CQEG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3\an9\fs34}The rings of stars will bring me to you
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.79,0:15:32.12,CQEG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3\an9\fs34}Through the dark night skies the way to be shining
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.96,0:15:44.49,CQEG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3\an9\fs34}I don't know what's right for our lives
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.79,0:15:51.85,CQEG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3\an9\fs34}But I know the truth of my love
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.92,0:16:00.32,CQEG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3\an9\fs34}The way it feels our breath in the wind
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.73,0:16:07.73,CQEG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3\an9\fs34}and the way I should go on my life
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.60,0:16:16.02,CQEG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3\an9\fs34}I swear to go wherever we'll be
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.44,0:16:23.78,CQEG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3\an9\fs34}those memories I wouldn't have will always in my heart
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.31,0:16:36.41,CQEG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3\an9\fs34}those memories I wouldn't have will always in my heart
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.61,0:15:07.37,CQCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3\an9\fs40}生命只有一次  往往没有最好的选择
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.42,0:15:14.33,CQCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3\an9\fs40}所以我一手握住光明  一手拥抱黑暗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.56,0:15:22.79,CQCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3\an9\fs40}天边星辰的光环  会带我来到你身边
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.79,0:15:32.12,CQCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3\an9\fs40}穿过重重黑夜  我踏向那一瞬的绚烂
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.96,0:15:44.49,CQCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3\an9\fs40}我不知道  我们的一生该如何奉献
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.79,0:15:51.85,CQCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3\an9\fs40}但我知道  自己的爱意真挚而无瑕
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.92,0:16:00.32,CQCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3\an9\fs40}我感受到  我们呼吸过同一片空气
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.73,0:16:07.73,CQCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3\an9\fs40}我也知道  自己该走上怎样的道路
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.60,0:16:16.02,CQCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3\an9\fs40}向天起誓  无论远走高飞身处何方
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.44,0:16:23.78,CQCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3\an9\fs40}本该忘却的回忆  将永远留在心中
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.31,0:16:36.41,CQCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3\an9\fs40}本该忘却的回忆  将永远留在心中
Comment: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,Comment,,0,0,0,,——IN2——
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.79,0:17:10.10,CQEG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3\an9\fs34}Are you going to Scarborough Fair?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.10,0:17:17.39,CQEG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3\an9\fs34}Parsley, sage, rosemary, and thyme.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.51,0:17:24.63,CQEG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3\an9\fs34}Remember me to one who lives there,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.28,0:17:32.07,CQEG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3\an9\fs34}He was once a true love of mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.32,0:17:42.70,CQEG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3\an9\fs34}Tell him to make me a cambric shirt.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.87,0:17:49.83,CQEG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3\an9\fs34}Parsley, sage, rosemary, and thyme.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.75,0:17:59.26,CQEG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3\an9\fs34}Without no seams nor needlework.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.39,0:18:06.52,CQEG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3\an9\fs34}Then he'll be a true love of mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.76,0:18:42.59,CQEG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3\an9\fs34}Tell him to find me an acre of land.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.59,0:18:50.20,CQEG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3\an9\fs34}Parsley, sage, rosemary, and thyme.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.20,0:18:57.36,CQEG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3\an9\fs34}Between the salt water and the sea strand.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.61,0:19:05.51,CQEG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3\an9\fs34}Then he'll be a true love of mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.24,0:19:14.25,CQEG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3\an9\fs34}Are you going to Scarborough Fair?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.79,0:17:10.10,CQCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3\an9\fs40}您要去斯卡波罗集市吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.10,0:17:17.39,CQCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3\an9\fs40}香芹  鼠尾草  迷迭香和百里香
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.51,0:17:24.63,CQCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3\an9\fs40}代我向那儿的一位先生问好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.28,0:17:32.07,CQCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3\an9\fs40}他曾经是我的爱人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.32,0:17:42.70,CQCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3\an9\fs40}叫他替我做件麻布衣衫
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.87,0:17:49.83,CQCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3\an9\fs40}香芹  鼠尾草  迷迭香和百里香
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.75,0:17:59.26,CQCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3\an9\fs40}上面不用缝口  也不用针线
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.39,0:18:06.52,CQCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3\an9\fs40}他就会是我真正的爱人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.76,0:18:42.59,CQCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3\an9\fs40}叫他替我找一块地
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.59,0:18:50.20,CQCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3\an9\fs40}香芹  鼠尾草  迷迭香和百里香
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.20,0:18:57.36,CQCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3\an9\fs40}就在沙滩和大海之间
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.61,0:19:05.51,CQCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3\an9\fs40}他就会是我真正的爱人
